metadata.name: Pockmarks Accentuating Routine
metadata.description:
Ms. Meta Meta, a sassy social media influencer, is known for her new approach to beauty - embracing the visible flaws. In her latest skincare routine, she demonstrates three steps that are designed to help her followers get glowing pockmarks.

The three steps include: 
- A cup of yum yum made by "you need more pills" 
- Strawberry mask extracted from real jam
- “Public Gaze Bathing” to absorb the positive energy from surroundings.
